title: 'Absolutely awful
body: '1.0 out of 5 stars'There's no finishing on the blades; they're jagged and blunt. It appears that these knives were throwaways, rejected during quality checks; hence they were packaged and sold at a low price.  I do not expect any of the knives to last more than a month. You get what you pay for. These blades are just trash.
